Clarke Leads Mickelson by Two Shots in Final Round of British Open Golf

-- B y   B o b   B e n s c h
-- 
2011-07-17T15:03:12Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-17/clarke-leads-mickelson-by-two-shots-in-final-round-of-british-open-golf.html
Darren Clarke leads  Phil Mickelson 
by one shot in the final round of golf’s  British Open .  Clarke is 2-under par through eight holes today at Royal
St. George’s in Sandiwch,  England , and 7-under overall. Four-
time major winner Mickelson is 6-under for both his round and
the tournament.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bob Bensch at 
 bbensch@bloomberg.net  